6.0.0-portable
Release Date: 2025-08-13
Platform: Intel Core Ultra 7 155H (Meteor Lake)
Microcode: Detection improved (>0x20 = AVX-512 cloaked)
Ubuntu: 24.04+ LiveCD
Claude Code: v1.0.77 (@anthropic-ai/claude-code)

Changes in 6.0.0:
- NEW: Portable installer (claude-portable-launch.sh)
- Everything in one directory (~300MB)
- Fixed AVX-512 cloaking detection
- Runtime AVX-512 test, not just cpuinfo
- Fixed npm package: @anthropic-ai/claude-code
- Added _GNU_SOURCE for CPU affinity
- Three installation methods
- Local Node.js option (no sudo needed)

Changes in 5.0.0:
- Changed from Claude CLI to Claude Code
- Added npm/node auto-installation
- Added God-tier statusline for all editors
- Nano as default editor with syntax highlighting
- First-launch helper with /config and /terminal-setup
- Local agents folder detection
- Enhanced shell prompt with project info
- 28 production agents with v7.0 framework